results.poem:
They ate turkey,
 mashed potatoes and PUMPKIN pie.
 They ate and ate and ate and ate, 
 and in the end, 
they fell ASLEEP on their PLATES!
results.translation: Comieron pavo, puré de patatas y pastel de CALABAZA. Comieron, comieron, comieron y comieron, y al final, ¡se quedaron DORMIDOS en sus PLATOS!
